&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An important function of the human brain is memory. &lt;br&gt;
Humans should use this for learning lessons. &lt;br&gt;
Unfortunately, it&amp;rsquo;s often used to create nostalgic moments in present life. &lt;br&gt;
Life only happens in present, it is neither past nor future. &lt;br&gt;
People love dwelling in the past, being nostalgic. &lt;br&gt;
Why? Because they avoid facing the present and fear the future. &lt;br&gt;
So, finding pleasure is only possible by living in the past.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
